  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nUser requested testing and demonstration of the Instagram Creator Marketplace MCP connector. Assistant explored the connector's capabilities, attempted live queries, and discovered that a linked Instagram Business Account is required for functionality. Despite authentication limitations, successfully documented the connector's schema and filtering capabilities in a structured brief.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nUser wanted to understand and test the Instagram Creator Marketplace connector functionality, specifically requesting live data examples and a capabilities overview.\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nExplored MCP connector tools, tested list_pages and creator search functions, documented API response structures, identified authentication requirements, and compiled a capability brief despite access limitations.\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [capability_brief] Instagram Creator Marketplace Connector Brief — Structured documentation of connector capabilities, filtering options, and implementation requirements\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Proceeded with schema exploration despite authentication limitations\n- Documented capabilities based on API structure rather than live data\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Schema introspection provided valuable capability insights\n- Clear identification of authentication requirements\nFailed / suboptimal:\n\n- Cannot demonstrate live data without proper Instagram Business Account linking\nDiscoveries:\n\n- Meta enforces strict page_id requirements for creator search\n- Connector has extensive demographic and interest filtering capabilities\n\n## Challenges & Blockers\n\n- No Instagram Business Account linked to Meta session\n- API requires valid page_id for all creator search operations\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- Should we link an Instagram Business Account for full testing?\n- What specific creator search use cases are most relevant?\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- Link Instagram Business Account if full testing desired\n- Review capability brief for implementation planning\n---\nUID: j9cSPPx9xjFd156thfS53Q | Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 | Cost: $0.0108\n"
